# Instagram / Meta Licensed Audio related domains for Surge
# Single-proxy version: use one policy group for this whole ruleset.
# Do NOT reject graph/gateway domains.

DOMAIN,graph.facebook.com
DOMAIN,graph.instagram.com
DOMAIN,gateway.instagram.com
DOMAIN,test-gateway.instagram.com

DOMAIN-SUFFIX,instagram.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,threads.net
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,threads.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,fbcdn.net
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,cdninstagram.com
